to use this easily as a exe you will need a python idle see my video how to download it from channel Tele Coder
then you will have to extract that folder not the game (it will not work if you extract only the game and tried to play)
extract that folder to the place you like 
then you will have to install pygame to download it follow these steps:
1 go to powershell and type pip if get any error then goto my channel Tele coder and solve it
2 if you got then type "pip install --user pygame"
3 then open that game and have fun!!!!
